    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The making of a design by pouring colored sands, powdered pigments from minerals or crystals, or pigments from other natural or synthetic sources onto a surface to make a fixed or unfixed image. They are often made on the ground or the floor rather than on a separate support. The works may be unfixed or fixed.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000079228/Grove Art Online (2008-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000114707/Oxford English Dictionary Online (2002-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>一種製造圖案的技術。將染色的沙子、從各種礦物或者水晶所提煉出的粉末狀顏料、抑或是其它天然或人工製成的顏料倒在一處表面上，以製作出固定或者不固定的圖像。沙畫通常是於地面上或者是地板上製作而成，而不是在一個獨立的支撐物上。這類作品兼有固定或可動的形態。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000079740/AS-Academia Sinica data (2014-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Het maken van een ontwerp door het strooien van gekleurd zand, pigmenten in poedervorm uit mineralen of kristallen, of pigmenten van andere natuurlijke of synthetische bronnen op een oppervlak, zodat een vaste of onvaste afbeelding ontstaat. Ze worden vaak op de grond of de vloer gemaakt en niet op een aparte drager. De werken kunnen vast of onvast zijn.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A confecção de um desenho despejando areias coloridas, pigmentos em pó de minerais ou cristais ou pigmentos de outras fontes naturais ou sintéticas sobre uma superfície para formar uma imagem fixa ou não fixa. Frequentemente, são feitos no solo ou no chão, e não em um suporte separado. As obras podem ser corrigidas ou não corrigidas.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Portuguese</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000316/CVAA-BR</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000109633/CVAA-BR Consortium (2020-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
